snippet.title: Derail Valley: Simulator - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Derail Valley on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/588030/Derail_Valley/

Derail Valley: Simulator is a free major update to Derail Valley. If you already own the game, it will automatically update.

Thank you for your support!
